===Noun===
'''taffy''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

# {{US}} A soft, chewy [[candy]] made from boiled [[molasses]] or [[brown sugar]].

===Usage notes===
*'''Taffy''' is similar to the British [[toffee]], which is a hard candy, but this is a soft candy in America.